modules.name: AWS.AppSync
modules.comments: AWS AppSync provides API actions for creating and interacting with data sources using GraphQL from your application.

declarations.comments: Creates a unique key that you can distribute to clients who are executing your API.
declarations.title: createApiKey

declarations.comments:
Creates a Resolver object.

A resolver converts incoming requests into a format that a data source can understand and converts the data source's responses into GraphQL.
declarations.title: createResolver

declarations.comments: Retrieves the introspection schema for a GraphQL API.
declarations.title: getIntrospectionSchema

declarations.comments: Retrieves the current status of a schema creation operation.
declarations.title: getSchemaCreationStatus

declarations.comments: Lists the API keys for a given API.
declarations.title: listApiKeys

declarations.comments: Lists the data sources for a given API.
declarations.title: listDataSources

declarations.comments: Lists the resolvers for a given API and type.
declarations.title: listResolvers

declarations.comments: Lists the types for a given API.
declarations.title: listTypes

declarations.comments:
Adds a new schema to your GraphQL API.

This operation is asynchronous. Use to determine when it has completed.
declarations.title: startSchemaCreation

declarations.comments: The API key exceeded a limit. Try your request again.
declarations.title: ApiKeyLimitExceededException

declarations.comments: The API key expiration must be set to a value between 1 and 365 days.
declarations.title: ApiKeyValidityOutOfBoundsException

declarations.comments: The GraphQL API exceeded a limit. Try your request again.
declarations.title: ApiLimitExceededException

declarations.comments: The request is not well formed. For example, a value is invalid or a required field is missing. Check the field values, and try again.
declarations.title: BadRequestException

declarations.comments: Another modification is being made. That modification must complete before you can make your change.
declarations.title: ConcurrentModificationException

declarations.comments: An internal AWS AppSync error occurred. Try your request again.
declarations.title: InternalFailureException

declarations.comments: The request exceeded a limit. Try your request again.
declarations.title: LimitExceededException

declarations.comments: The resource specified in the request was not found. Check the resource and try again.
declarations.title: NotFoundException

declarations.comments: You are not authorized to perform this operation.
declarations.title: UnauthorizedException

declarations.comments: Describes an Amazon Cognito User Pool configuration.
declarations.title: UserPoolConfig
